  "detailed_description": "Fired and blackballed by Chef Hamsey, you are a chef looking to find your next position. Unfortunately, the employees of any restaurant you walk into want you dead! Utilise a food-themed upgrade tree that allows for focused or balanced builds. It's up to you to prove you're worthy of the job!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Off Hordes Of Enemies!</strong></h2>Fight unique chef enemies, each with their own attack! Can you dodge chefs, plates, and sushi knives? Includes a mix and match mode so any level can spawn any enemy or boss! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tackle the head chefs in epic boss fights!</strong></h2>Angry that you're killing all their chefs, fend off multiple bosses, unique to each level!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade your stats to insanity with huge bullets and many more options!</strong></h2>Increase your damage, critical skills, bullet sizes, elemental damage, and more!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fully customiseable difficulty settings! How do you want to play?</strong></h2>Do you want fast enemies with low health? How about super difficult bosses? Or enough damage to kill you in one hit? <strong>Too Many Cooks</strong> has a customiseable difficulty setting, so you can make it as tough as you want!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Multiple restaurant locations to choose from, each with their own unique enemies and bosses</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Interchangeable characters and weapons</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Food themed upgrade system that allows for focused or balanced builds</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Permanent upgrade system and unlockable recipe upgrades</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Both preset difficulty levels as well as a fully customiseable difficulty system. You choose how you play!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*A mix and match system to make every run unique--chance to spawn any enemy or boss in every level!</ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Fired and blackballed by Chef Hamsey, you are a chef looking to find your next position. Unfortunately, the employees of any restaurant you walk into want you dead! Utilise a food-themed upgrade tree that allows for focused or balanced builds. It's up to you to prove you're worthy of the job!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight Off Hordes Of Enemies!</strong></h2>Fight unique chef enemies, each with their own attack! Can you dodge chefs, plates, and sushi knives? Includes a mix and match mode so any level can spawn any enemy or boss! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/2f1236eeca6882fbd3bb72051db01bd7.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tackle the head chefs in epic boss fights!</strong></h2>Angry that you're killing all their chefs, fend off multiple bosses, unique to each level!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/f6da5b634aa51cd064df787e0dd6788b.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade your stats to insanity with huge bullets and many more options!</strong></h2>Increase your damage, critical skills, bullet sizes, elemental damage, and more!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/56d0f47222ea28002c7b62e32986d9ef.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fully customiseable difficulty settings! How do you want to play?</strong></h2>Do you want fast enemies with low health? How about super difficult bosses? Or enough damage to kill you in one hit? <strong>Too Many Cooks</strong> has a customiseable difficulty setting, so you can make it as tough as you want!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.poster.avif?t=1710157983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.webm?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568030/extras/5a87bd14c3ebd0f09e9c80ad45b27531.mp4?t=1710157983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Multiple restaurant locations to choose from, each with their own unique enemies and bosses</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Interchangeable characters and weapons</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Food themed upgrade system that allows for focused or balanced builds</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Permanent upgrade system and unlockable recipe upgrades</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*Both preset difficulty levels as well as a fully customiseable difficulty system. You choose how you play!</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">*A mix and match system to make every run unique--chance to spawn any enemy or boss in every level!</ul>",
